* &quot;Monsieur&quot; (the German song with Italian lyrics by Vito Pallavicini) (1962, No.1)
* &quot;Sul mio carro (Chariot)&quot; (1962, No.1)
* &quot;Quelli che hanno un cuore (Anyone who had a heart)&quot; (1964, No.4)
